plyTime":"2019-10-23T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"係呀, 其實831 之後全香港人已經撤夜換走晒, 真香港人已經無論黃綠藍全體用石頭綁住沉晒落大嶼山附近海床, 好似話可以幫政府慳返幾億填海費<br />\n<br />\n今日既700萬香港人全部都係解放軍同共黨黨員係831 至901期間搭旅遊巴落黎香港扮架, 果晚係黃崗對面個山頭睇住14萬架旅遊巴秘密過關, 條龍由黃崗排到上廣洲<br />\n<br />\n你都係唔信既話望下林鄭同何妖既現場直播, 將個鏡頭放大8000倍一睇, 上網對一對就知其實係吉林省黨立演藝學院學員二年班生扮架啦!<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗咁多啦, 樓主你係最後既真香港人倖存者, 見到呢個msg 好快d 走, 你屋企樓下已經有架黑van, 4個國安落左車係出面升降機大堂等緊你<br />\n<br />\n我係邊個? 我咪就係果4個裡面其中一個囉, 開門啦柒頭!<br />\n<br />\n#已FC<br />\n#本故事純粹虛構不過連仔應該會信十足"},{"pid":"b1e8fc5f728fa437e971e1e15247211fcfab8fa9","tid":1670521,"uid":203797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f820aae847aa5f01dfe7137ab75e543c0a1f9e","tid":1670521,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74da4c760fa028a6c5bea9a310fd7b5f80c5553c","tid":1670521,"uid":35930,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:27:24.000Z","msg":"樓主肯定冇同囡囡自拍過<br />\n<br />\n恥笑開始"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}